Pre-Game Insights: Lee Carsley is the new head coach for England, preparing for his first major assignment in the UEFA Nations League.
The match is significant as the second England game at Wembley in the 2024 competition, expected to draw large support.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Wembley Stadium is most conveniently accessed via public transport, including train, bus, tube, and pedestrian routes.
Disabled persons should contact Wembley Stadium for reservations.
Others: Membership benefits for England Supporters Travel Club and My England Football Club include priority ticketing and discounts.
Hospitality packages vary in price and include access to VIP lounges and executive dining.
